ur knees and thighs, extending into your hips and pelvis.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 35.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "From your core, let your awareness flow down through your hands and arms, to your fingertips.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 30.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Now, bring your attention up into your shoulders, neck, and throat. This can be a common area for holding worry.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 40.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Without trying to change anything, simply acknowledge any tightness, clenching, or holding in this region.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 45.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Allow a gentle breath to flow into these areas, simply noticing what is present.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 40.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Now, move your awareness to your abdomen and chest, observing the subtle movements of your breath here.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 40.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Notice any sensations of churning, emptiness, or constriction within your belly or chest.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 45.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Move your awareness to your heart space, sensing its rhythm, any feelings of openness or tightness.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 40.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Finally, bring your awareness to your face and head.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 20.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Explore the jaw, temples, forehead, and behind the eyes for any subtle clenching or tension.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 40.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "As you continue to scan, if your mind wanders or you encounter areas of intense discomfort, simply acknowledge them as sensations.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 30.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "There is no need to fix or push away. Just allow them to be present, held in gentle awareness.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 50.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Notice how simply acknowledging a sensation, rather than resisting it, can shift your relationship to it.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 60.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Let your awareness rest gently on the entire body, from head to toe, as a field of sensation.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 60.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Gently expand your awareness to include your entire body once more, resting in the felt sense of presence.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Feel the body as a whole, held by the earth, breathing. Take a moment to absorb the wisdom gained from this quiet exploration, understanding that acknowledging physical sensations of anxiety with gentle awareness truly can begin to release tension.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 4.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "As this practice comes to a close, remember that the wisdom of your body is always available to you as an anchor amidst the storm.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "The journey on 'Calm Amidst the Storm' continues. Carry this gentle awareness and compassion into the rest of your day.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Thank you for walking this step of the path with me today.", "duration": null}]	https://senda-ai.s3.amazonaws.com/audio/53_Exploring_the_Bodys_Wisdom_of_Worry_DuEYstirjM.mp3	2025-12-18 17:20:30.879646	\N	2025-12-18 13:12:52.535375+00	2025-12-18 17:23:00.249859+00
