ss, not to dissect it or push it away, but simply to acknowledge it as an experience.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Now, we will offer it kindness.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Repeat silently to yourself, or simply hold the intention: May I be safe.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 25.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "May I be at ease.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 25.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "May I be free from suffering.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 25.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Direct these wishes of kindness towards yourself, the one experiencing this feeling of anxiety. Allow a warmth to spread through your chest, or wherever compassion arises for you.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 30.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Now, let's offer this same kindness directly to the feeling of anxiety itself.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "May this feeling be met with kindness.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 35.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "May this tension soften.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 35.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "May I hold this experience with compassion.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 35.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "You are not trying to make the anxiety disappear, but rather to change your relationship to it. To see it not as an enemy, but as a part of your present experience that can be held with tenderness.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 40.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "If your mind wanders, or if judgment arises towards the anxiety, simply notice this. This too, is part of the process.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Gently return to the intention of kindness. Say to yourself: 'It's okay to feel this. May I be kind to this moment.'", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 45.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Continue to offer the phrases, allowing them to resonate in the space where anxiety manifests, or simply to fill your awareness with this intention.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "May I be at ease.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "May this feeling be met with kindness.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 60.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "With each breath, imagine creating a gentle space around the feeling, a space of acceptance and warmth, rather than resistance.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 50.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "As we begin to bring this practice to a close, gently expand your awareness from the specific feeling of anxiety to your entire body.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Notice the steady rhythm of your breath, anchoring you to the present moment. Feel the contact points with your seat, the ground beneath you.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 10.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Remember, this act of meeting anxiety with compassion is a powerful step towards transforming its presence, allowing you to access the wisdom it may carry, rather than being overwhelmed by its message.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 3.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "As this practice ends, the journey continues. Carry this awareness of self-compassion with you, knowing it's a vital inner resource on your path to calm amidst life's storms. Thank you for walking this step of the path with me today.", "duration": null}]	https://senda-ai.s3.amazonaws.com/audio/54_Befriending_Difficult_Emotions_XnRqkG6zrU.mp3	2025-12-18 13:37:44.457523	\N	2025-12-18 13:12:52.540132+00	2025-12-18 17:23:01.640033+00
