ht simply note 'worrying' or 'anxiety thought'.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 30.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "The label is not to judge the thought, but to acknowledge its presence.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "And then, with kindness, let it go.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Allow it to simply pass, like a cloud drifting across the sky.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Return your awareness to the anchor of your breath, or the sensations in your body.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 40.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "There's no need to engage with every story your mind creates.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Especially with anxious thoughts, which often present themselves as urgent facts.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Simply observe.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Note.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "And release.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 45.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "You are not your thoughts.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "You are the awareness that observes them.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 30.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "If you find yourself caught in a strong current of thought, gently acknowledge it.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Perhaps a 'strong thinking' or 'absorbed in worry'.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "And then, with compassion, redirect your attention.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Back to the breath.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Back to the body.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 50.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "This spaciousness you are cultivating is a profound freedom.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "It is the understanding that thoughts, even anxious ones, are transient mental events, not definitive realities.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 40.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Now, gently begin to broaden your awareness.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Feel the presence of your body again, sensing the touch of air on your skin, the sounds around you.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 3.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Remember the key insight from our practice today: thoughts are not facts, and you can choose not to identify with every anxious narrative that arises.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "This discerning awareness is a powerful tool in developing robust inner resources to navigate anxiety with greater clarity, compassion, and presence, as we seek to transform our relationship with worry and stress.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "As this session closes, the path continues\\u2014carry this clarity with you. Thank you for sharing this step with me.", "duration": null}]	https://senda-ai.s3.amazonaws.com/audio/55_Navigating_the_River_of_Anxious_Thoughts_sNN6H6DDRE.mp3	2025-12-18 13:37:57.970902	\N	2025-12-18 13:12:52.543536+00	2025-12-18 17:28:43.218273+00
