ove.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "And they pass.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 100.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "You are the sky itself: vast, unchanging, unmarred.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Rest in this open, spacious awareness.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "No need to grasp.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "No need to push away.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 110.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Simply notice what arises.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Allow it to be there.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "And let it go.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 100.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "This open space is your inherent resilience.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "It is always present.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 120.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "When anxiety arises, as it naturally will, do not resist it.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Instead, make space for it within this vast awareness.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Allow it to be a cloud in your sky.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 105.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Notice its qualities.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Its texture.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Its movement.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 95.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "And then, gently release the focus, returning to the vastness of the sky itself.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "To the spaciousness beneath.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 115.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "You are not your anxiety.", "duration": null}, {"type"