dering mind, not through force, but through gentle understanding.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 60.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Continue this gentle dance.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Open awareness.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Noticing.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Acknowledging.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Releasing.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Returning.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 60.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Be patient with yourself.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Cultivate an attitude of understanding and compassion.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "There is no right or wrong way for the mind to behave.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Only the opportunity to observe and practice this gentle redirection.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 60.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Each moment of noticing is a success.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Each gentle return is a step forward on your path.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 60.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Allow your awareness to deepen.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Rest in the space of knowing.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 60.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "As we begin to bring this period of formal practice to a close...", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Gently broaden your awareness to include the sounds around you, the feeling of the air on your skin.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Bring your attention back more fully to the sensation of your body in contact with what supports it.", "duration": null}, {"type": "pause", "content": null, "duration": 5.0}, {"type"