ull, "duration": 2.0}, {"type": "speak", "content": "Carry this understanding and this newfound rhythm into your day. These short bursts, when practiced consistently, will transform your ability to concentrate and bring greater presence to all areas of your life.", "duration": null}, {"type": "speak", "content": "This practice ends, and the journey goes on. Take this awareness with you\\u2014thank you for walking this part of the path today.", "duration": null}]	https://senda-ai.s3.amazonaws.com/audio/75_The_Power_of_Short_Bursts_Deep_Work_Intervals_D35JSuJAbd.mp3	2025-12-18 21:58:54.545667	\N	2025-12-18 18:37:42.822021+00	2025-12-18 22:05:16.950971+00
